description: Welcome to the best 3 bed deal in South Boston! This beautifully maintained 3 bed/2 bath townhouse offers four levels of thoughtfully designed living space in one of the city's most vibrant and rapidly developing neighborhoods. Whether you're a buyer seeking a turnkey home or an investor capitalizing on the area's impressive growth this move-in ready condo is a standout opportunity. Features include a semi-open floor plan featuring a sun-drenched top-floor primary bedroom with master bath, a large living room space, and modern kitchen with updated appliances. Additional highlights include gleaming hardwood and carpeted flooring, central heating, in-unit laundry, private back deck, and two deed parking spaces. With easy access to shops, restaurants, public transit, and new development all around, this is a smart buy in a prime location. Don't miss it! New high efficiency boiler (2019) and new windows and trim (2019). Newer siding (2016).
